       <p class="project-description">
        A comprehensive open-source voxel game developed over several years. Built from the ground up using 
        <strong>Java</strong> and <strong>LWJGL (OpenGL)</strong>, the project features a custom rendering 
        pipeline and complex world-generation algorithms.
    </p>

    <div class="feature-container">
      Features include:
        <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><strong>Systems:</strong> LAN Multiplayer, Day/Night cycles, and Random Tick Events.</li>
            <li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Real-time Torch and Sun light propagation logic.</li>
            <li><strong>Physics:</strong> Fire spreading mechanics and falling gravity-affected blocks (Sand/Gravel).</li>
            <li><strong>Agriculture:</strong> Dynamic crop growth and Amethyst crystal maturation systems.</li>
            <li><strong>Exploration:</strong> Procedural unique biomes, cave systems, and ore distribution.</li>
            <li><strong>Transportation:</strong> Functional Minecart rail systems and navigable boats.</li>
            <li><strong>Fauna:</strong> Diverse entity AI (Dogs, Cats, Foxes, Beavers) with biome-specific spawning.</li>
            <li><strong>Survival:</strong> Survival crafting, loot tables, recipes and furnace and storage blocks.</li>
        </ul>
